{"type": "article", "id": 20898, "title": "几何圆桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-19T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122314dtrVXi1pZmWfL6Be.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这张圆桌有一个不可思议的平衡，像是将圆形桌面立在了圆锥的尖头上，只有俯下身才能看到桌子的下面和底座的连接。整张桌子只有底座和桌面两个部分，颜色单一，也没有其余的装饰，突出了它们之间的几何感，像一个小的雕塑。既有古典的纯净，也有现代的几何美感。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150642lX59wmaHh081Ecuf.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"687\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261506439fj4kcebEt3q6JIs.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"331\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261506435vRdoWB27i8C63pI.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150643TANa8qzUlhcZSQJd.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"801\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}